  "texts": [
    "Scores will be compared across groups to evaluate strategic prompting (H4).",
    " Thematic coding of GPT session logs will identify patterns in prompting, code generation, debugging, and test-related behaviours.",
    " Open-ended survey responses will be analysed to capture perceived challenges, strategies, and reflections on GPT and TDD.",
    " Findings from code artefacts, prompt logs, and survey responses will be triangulated to provide a holistic view of how TDD and GPT influence learning, strategy, and coding behaviour.",
    "This methodology builds on research demonstrating that TDD supports systematic thinking and reduces omission errors, particularly in novice programming contexts (Beck, 2003; George & Williams, 2004)."
